# Security Report Generator ‚Äî v2.0

## Architecture

```
project/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ report_engine.py   ‚Üê ‚òÖ CENTRALIZED ENGINE (all report logic lives here)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ gui_app.py         ‚Üê PyQt6 GUI  (imports report_engine)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ main.py            ‚Üê CLI wrapper (imports report_engine)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ build_exe.spec     ‚Üê PyInstaller build config
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ templates/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ web_template.docx
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ api_template.docx
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ mobile_template.docx
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ src/
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ excel_reader.py
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ poc_finder.py
```

### Key design principle

**`report_engine.py` is the single source of truth.**  
GUI, CLI, scripts, scheduled jobs ‚Äî all call the same `ReportEngine` class.  
No logic is duplicated. Bug fixes and new features only need to be made in one place.

